        <h2 class="text-center" style="letter-spacing: 3px; font-weight: bolder;"><i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true" style="color: #404895"></i><i class="fa fa-caret-left" aria-hidden="true" style="color: #d84f45"></i> The aims of the charity Mayaa HK <i class="fa fa-caret-right" aria-hidden="true" style="color: #404895"></i><i class="fa fa-caret-left" aria-hidden="true" style="color: #d84f45"></i></h2>
